OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776276673
OL,3,CTwo people die and third person in
OL,4,Chospital after car hits tree
OL,6,FTwo people have died and a third
OL,7,Fperson is in hospital after a car hit
OL,8,Fa tree near Consett.
OL,10,FPolice were called to School Lane, on
OL,11,Fthe north side of Derwent Reservoir,
OL,12,Fshortly before 6pm on Sunday evening
OL,13,F(12 April).
OL,15,FA Volkswagen Polo was travelling
OL,16,Fnorthbound on the road, which lies on
OL,17,Fthe Northumberland side of the border
OL,18,Fwith County Durham, when it left the
OL,19,Froad and hit a tree.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
