CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776276673
OL,3,CTwo people die and third person in
OL,4,Chospital after car hits tree
OL,6,FTwo people who were in the vehicle - a
OL,7,Fman in his 20s and a woman in her late
OL,8,Fteens - died at the scene.
OL,10,FThe third person who was in the
OL,11,Fvehicle - another man in his 20s - was
OL,12,Ftaken to hospital for treatment where
OL,13,Fhe remains in a stable condition.
OL,15,FPolice have launched an investigation,
OL,16,Fand are urging any witnesses to come
OL,17,Fforward.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
