PN,42803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776276673
OL,3,CTwo people die and third person in
OL,4,Chospital after car hits tree
OL,6,FSergeant Craig Bartle, of Northumbria
OL,7,FPolice, said: "Our thoughts are firmly
OL,8,Fwith the family and loved ones of the
OL,9,Fman and woman who have sadly died as a
OL,10,Fresult of this traffic incident.
OL,12,F"We will continue to offer their loved
OL,13,Fones all of the support they need as
OL,14,Fwe begin our investigations and seek
OL,15,Fto provide them with answers."
OL,17,FSgt Bartle added: "We are now
OL,18,Fappealing for any information and in
OL,19,Fparticular, anyone with dashcam
OL,20,Ffootage of the incident, or the
OL,21,Fmoments leading up to it.
OL,26,@oD@OOUtD@AOUwD@^O]yD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
