PN,42804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776276673
OL,3,CTwo people die and third person in
OL,4,Chospital after car hits tree
OL,6,F"We are particularly keen to speak
OL,7,Fwith anyone who was travelling in the
OL,8,Farea in either direction and who may
OL,9,Fhave seen what happened.
OL,11,F"If this was you, or you were in the
OL,12,Farea around the time of this
OL,13,Fcollision, please come forward and
OL,14,Fspeak with us.
OL,16,F"Any information you are able to
OL,17,Fprovide could prove crucial to our
OL,18,Fenquiries."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOUzD@KO]
